\c 23
\s Jobho anochema kuti awane Mwari, kuti agone kuzvirevera amene kwaari, nokuti anoziva kuti haana mhosva
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Jobho akapindura, akati:
\v 2 Kunyange nanhasi ndinonyunyuta ndine shungu; kurohwa kwangu kwakanyanya kukunda kugomera kwangu.
\v 3 Haiwa! Dai ndaiziva kwandingamuwana, kuti ndisvike ipo pachigaro chake.
\v 4 Ndairondedzera mhaka yangu pamberi pake, ndaizadza muromo wangu nenharo.
\v 5 Ndaiziva mashoko aanopindura nawo, ndainzwisisa zvaanondiudza.
\v 6 Angaita nharo neni nesimba rake guru here? Kwete; asi angandirangarira.
\v 7 Apo akarurama angataurirana naye; kuti ndisunungurwe nokusingaperi pamutongi wangu.
\v 8 Tarira, ndinopfuura mberi, asi haapo; uuye shure, asi handimuoni.
\v 9 Nokuruoko rworuboshwe, kana achibata, asi handigoni kumuona; anozvivanza paruoko rworudyi, kuti ndirege kumuona.
\v 10 Nokuti iye anoziva nzira yandinofamba nayo; kana akandiidza, ndichabuda ndakaita sendarama.
\v 11 Rutsoka rwangu rwakaramba ruchitsika paakatsika iye; ndakarambira panzira yake, handina kutsauka.
\v 12 Handina kubva pamurairo wemiromo yake; ndakachengeta sefuma mashoko omuromo wake kupfuura mugove wangu.
\v 13 Asi iye anorangarira chinhu chimwe, ndianiko angamudzora? Zvinoda moyo wake, ndizvo zvaanoita.
\v 14 Nokuti anoita zvandakatemerwa; nezvinhu zvizhinji zvakadai zviri kwaari.
\v 15 Saka ndinotambudzika pamberi pake; kana ndichimufunga ndinomutya.
\v 16 Nokuti Mwari akatorera moyo wangu simba, Wemasimbaose akandivhundusa.
\v 17 Nokuti handina kuparadzwa nekuda kwerima, kana nokuda kwerima guru rakafukidza chiso changu.
